---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
const title = "SocialProof for Mortgage Brokers — Turn Closed Loans Into Future Clients";
const description = "Homebuyers research mortgage brokers extensively before calling. Brokers with visible client testimonials get more qualified leads and close more loans. SocialProof makes it simple.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="badge">For Mortgage Brokers</div>
        <h1>Every smooth closing is a story that sells your next loan.</h1>
        <p class="subhead">First-time homebuyers and refinancers are terrified of the process. When they find a broker with real client stories describing a smooth, stress-free experience — they stop shopping. SocialProof helps you capture and display those stories automatically.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-btn">Start free — no credit card</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain-points">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why mortgage brokers need strong testimonials</h2>
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="icon">😰</div>
            <h3>Borrowers are anxious buyers</h3>
            <p>A mortgage is the largest financial decision most people make. They need proof — not just that you're competent, but that you communicate, advocate, and deliver when it matters most.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="icon">🏦</div>
            <h3>Competing against banks with brand recognition</h3>
            <p>Big banks have marketing budgets. Independent brokers have better service. Testimonials are how that service advantage becomes visible to people who've never heard of you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="icon">🔍</div>
            <h3>Prospects research before they reach out</h3>
            <p>Homebuyers spend weeks researching. If your website or referral profile doesn't have recent, specific testimonials, you lose leads before the conversation even starts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How SocialProof works for mortgage brokers</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">1</div>
            <div class="step-body">
              <h3>Send your collection link at closing</h3>
              <p>The day your client gets their keys is when they're most grateful. That's the perfect moment to send your SocialProof link. A short text with your link converts extremely well.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">2</div>
            <div class="step-body">
              <h3>Capture the emotional story</h3>
              <p>Guided prompts help borrowers describe what was stressful, how you helped, and what the result felt like. Stories that mention first home, fast closing, or rate shopping help future clients self-identify.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-num">3</div>
            <div class="step-body">
              <h3>Display testimonials where leads convert</h3>
              <p>Embed a widget on your website, your Zillow/Realtor profile bio, and your rate quote page. Social proof placed before a form dramatically increases completions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonial-example">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The testimonial that turns a browser into a borrower</h2>
        <blockquote>
          "As first-time buyers, we were completely overwhelmed. Our broker explained every step clearly, got us a rate lower than we expected, and we closed in 28 days. At our final walkthrough I literally cried. I'm recommending her to every person I know buying a home."
          <cite>— First-time homebuyer, 30-year fixed</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="note">Specific details — 28 days to close, first-time buyer, lower rate — make this testimonial far more convincing than generic praise.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start building your testimonial library today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Your next referral is already Googling you — give them a reason to call.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-btn">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>

<style>
  .for-page { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e6b 0%, #1a2545 100%); color: white; padding: 5rem 0 4rem; text-align: center; }
  .badge { display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 20px; padding: 0.35rem 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 1.2rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .subhead { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #e67e22; color: white; padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: #ca6f1e; }
  .pain-points { padding: 4rem 0; background: #f9f8ff; }
  .pain-points h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.8rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
  .icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.6rem; }
  .card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .how-it-works { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .how-it-works h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .step-num { background: #2c3e6b; color: white; width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .step-body h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.4rem; }
  .step-body p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .testimonial-example { padding: 4rem 0; background: #f9f8ff; }
  .testimonial-example h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  blockquote { background: white; border-left: 4px solid #2c3e6b; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  cite { display: block; font-style: normal; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; margin-top: 0.8rem; }
  .note { text-align: center; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #666; margin: 0; }
  .cta-section { padding: 4rem 0; text-align: center; }
  .cta-section h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-section p { font-size: 1rem; color: #555; max-width: 550px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
</style>
